OL,3,CKyle Clifford pleads guilty to three
OL,4,Ccounts of murder
OL,6,FA 26-year-old man who fatally shot his
OL,7,Fex-girlfriend and her sister with a
OL,8,Fcrossbow before stabbing their
OL,10,Fmother to death has pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Ftheir murders.
OL,13,FKyle Clifford tied 25-year-old former
OL,14,Fpartner Louise Hunt's arms and ankles
OL,15,Fwith duct tape and shot her through
OL,16,Fthe chest with a crossbow bolt at the
OL,17,Ffamily home in the quiet cul-de-sac of
OL,18,FAshlyn Close in Bushey, Hertfordshire,
OL,19,Fin July.
