OL,3,CKyle Clifford pleads guilty to three
OL,4,Ccounts of murder
OL,6,FMs Hunt's 61-year-old mother Carol
OL,7,FHunt, the wife of BBC commentator John
OL,8,FHunt, sustained significant stab
OL,9,Fwounds to her knee, hands, back and
OL,10,Ftorso following the attack by Clifford
OL,11,Fwith a 10in butcher's knife.
OL,13,FHannah Hunt, 28, was found in the main
OL,14,Fdoorway of the house with a crossbow
OL,15,Fbolt to the chest and was still alive
OL,16,Fwhen police arrived at the property at
OL,17,Faround 7.10pm on July 9.
