OL,6,FPolice had been called by Hannah Hunt,
OL,7,Fwho told officers she feared she was
OL,8,Fgoing to die as she had been shot and
OL,9,Fher sister and mother had also been
OL,10,Fattacked.
OL,12,FClifford, who served in the military
OL,13,Ffrom 2019 for around three years,
OL,14,Fbecame the subject of a manhunt for a
OL,15,Fnumber of hours before he was found
OL,16,Finjured in Lavender Hill Cemetery in
OL,17,FEnfield, north London, after shooting
OL,18,Fhimself in the chest with the crossbow.
