OL,3,CKyle Clifford pleads guilty to three
OL,4,Ccounts of murder
OL,6,FAppearing via video link at Cambridge
OL,7,FCrown Court on Wednesday, Clifford
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to three counts of
OL,9,Fmurder, one of false imprisonment
OL,10,Fagainst Louise Hunt, and two counts of
OL,11,Fpossession of offensive weapons ` the
OL,12,Fcrossbow and the knife.
OL,14,FHe pleaded not guilty to a charge of
OL,15,Fraping Louise Hunt.
OL,17,FFollowing the attacks, the Home Office
OL,18,Fsaid Home Secretary Yvette Cooper was
OL,19,Furgently considering whether tougher
OL,20,Fcrossbow laws were needed.
